(201, 1, '2024-05-28 12:46:50', '2024-05-28 04:46:50', '<div id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\r\n<div class=\"breadcrumbs\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" width=\"200\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"course.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-50\" src=\"http://192.168.10.56/food06/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/course.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"226\" />\r\n<strong>選用澳洲和牛舌根的部位，此部位油脂均勻</strong>\r\n<strong>、肥瘦得宜，炙燒後漫佈在口中的細緻油花</strong>\r\n<strong>，以及軟中帶脆的彈性口感，令人著迷不已</strong>\r\n<strong>。</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"steak-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-88\" src=\"http://192.168.10.56/food06/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/steak-300x225-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n<strong>在燒肉店中使用Prime級的高級無骨牛小排</strong>\r\n<strong>，是相當大膽的舉動。完美分佈的油花，見</strong>\r\n<strong>其細膩的紋路就會怦然心動，是到店必點的</strong>\r\n<strong>明星商品。</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-78\" src=\"http://192.168.10.56/food06/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/seafood-300x225-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n<strong>限量供應的野生嚴選巨明蝦，肥厚飽滿的蝦</strong>\r\n<strong>身炙烤後口感脆彈，蘊藏其中濃濃的海洋鮮</strong>\r\n<strong>味，堪稱絕品！越來越稀少的珍貴滋味，非</strong>\r\n<strong>嚐不可。</strong></td>\r\n<td><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-76\" src=\"http://192.168.10.56/food06/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/pork-300x225-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n<strong>選用最珍貴的豬頸肉，特有的爽脆嚼勁以及</strong>\r\n<strong>高雅的油脂香氣，使人對豬肉的既有想法完</strong>\r\n<strong>全改觀，在高水準的燒肉食材中是稱霸一方</strong>\r\n<strong>的王者。</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-68\" src=\"http://192.168.10.56/food06/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/hotate-300x225-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n<strong>擁有生食等級，從北海道進口的嚴選巨干貝</strong>\r\n<strong>，閃閃發亮的水潤外表，是新鮮水產的最佳</strong>\r\n<strong>證明。微炙後的甘甜、細嫩，欲罷不能的極</strong>\r\n<strong>上美味。</strong></td>\r\n<td><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-90\" src=\"http://192.168.10.56/food06/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/vege011-300x225-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n<strong>啖燒肉也要有多種蔬菜均衡一下，拼盤內有</strong>\r\n<strong>帶殼的新鮮玉米筍、含水量高的雪白精靈菇</strong>\r\n<strong>、脆甜多汁的洋蔥與甜椒，轉換味蕾的最佳</strong>\r\n<strong>選擇！</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"course_1_l.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-51\" src=\"http://192.168.10.56/food06/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/course_1_l.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"226\" />\r\n<strong>厚切的極品沙朗，取自於CAB認證的安格斯</strong>\r\n<strong>牛，中央的沙朗心烤至5~7之間的熟度即可</strong>\r\n<strong>食用，週圍油脂豐足的的沙朗蓋可烤久些，</strong>\r\n<strong>別有風味。</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"course_2_l.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-52\" src=\"http://192.168.10.56/food06/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/course_2_l.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"226\" />\r\n<strong>選用頂級的澳洲和牛，大理石紋般的漂亮油</strong>\r\n<strong>花頗為誘人！優質的和牛肉不需烤炙過久，</strong>\r\n<strong>才能體會滑嫩肉質與迸發的鮮甜肉汁有多麼</strong>\r\n<strong>美妙。</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"MG_0554.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-71\" src=\"http://192.168.10.56/food06/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/MG_0554.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n<strong>季節蔬果沙拉，沙拉相當新鮮，海帶芽很脆</strong>\r\n<strong>嫩，淋上和風醬汁格外爽口。</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"MG_0558.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-72\" src=\"http://192.168.10.56/food06/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/MG_0558.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n<strong>牛小排，烤起來油脂細膩，口感香嫩。和牛</strong>\r\n<strong>肉質軟嫩，油花分布平均，可搭配玫瑰鹽吃</strong>\r\n<strong>。特選的牛里肌，油花比較多，服務生建議</strong>\r\n<strong>包生菜配胡麻、泡菜，可以降低油膩感。</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"MG_0576.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-73\" src=\"http://192.168.10.56/food06/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/MG_0576.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n<strong>霜降豬、梅花豬和雞腿肉拼盤。雞腿肉肉質</strong>\r\n<strong>鮮嫩，烤焦一點，別有一番風味。</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"MG_0590.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-74\" src=\"http://192.168.10.56/food06/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/MG_0590.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n<strong>精選海鮮中好吃沒話說的大蝦，肉厚彈實，</strong>\r\n<strong>海味濃郁。</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div id=\"post-6\" class=\"post-6 page type-page status-publish hentry\">\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<div class=\"addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style \">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"fb-like fb_iframe_widget\" style=\"height: 25px;\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-show_faces=\"false\" data-share=\"false\" data-action=\"like\" data-width=\"90\" data-height=\"25\" data-font=\"arial\" data-href=\"http://www.richiego.tw/cloud/10210/cvtc02/food/?page_id=6\" data-send=\"false\"></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"tweet_iframe_widget\" style=\"width: 62px; height: 25px;\"><iframe id=\"twitter-widget-0\" class=\"twitter-share-button twitter-share-button-rendered twitter-tweet-button\" style=\"position: absolute; visibility: hidden; width: 0px; height: 0px;\" title=\"Twitter Tweet Button\" src=\"http://http://platform.twitter.com/platform.twitter.com/widgets/tweet_button.57ff0b891fe1c9c735cbb440e7fd97ef.zh-tw.html#dnt=false&amp;id=twitter-widget-0&amp;lang=zh-tw&amp;original_referer=http%3A%2F%2F192.168.10.201%2Ffood%2F-page_id%3D6.htm&amp;size=m&amp;text=%E6%8E%A8%E8%96%A6%E8%8F%9C%E5%96%AE%20&amp;time=1716862614351&amp;type=share&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.richiego.tw%2Fcloud%2F10210%2Fcvtc02%2Ffood%2F%3Fpage_id%3D6\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" data-url=\"http://www.richiego.tw/cloud/10210/cvtc02/food/?page_id=6\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"comments\" class=\"hideme\">\r\n<p class=\"nocomments2\"></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- #comments -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '推薦菜單', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '179-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-05-28 12:46:50', '2024-05-28 04:46:50', '', 179, 'http://192.168.10.79/food028/?p=