n></span>\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"font-size: large;\">臨近都會公園、東海大學、逢甲商圈、秋紅谷吃飯逛街踏青都方便</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: small;\">。</span></b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-family: 標楷體; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"background-color: #800000;\">經營理念</span></span><b></b>\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"font-size: large;\">服務團隊<strong>：</strong>以「顧客滿意度」制定餐飲服務決策，並做為同仁管理培訓的最高指導原則，</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: large;\">隨時實踐最高顧客滿意度。總管理中心<strong>：</strong>包含營運、行銷企劃、人力資源、財務、研發</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: large;\">中心、總經理室等各部門，有效地統籌企業體的經營並推動運作的順暢。未來展望<strong>：</strong>規</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: large;\">劃朝多元化發展，將陸續推出新品牌、新風格、新菜系，十年之內，要挑戰成為世界級燒</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: large;\">肉餐飲連鎖集團。</span></b>\r\n<div class=\"addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style \">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"fb-like fb_iframe_widget\" style=\"height: 25px;\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-show_faces=\"false\" data-share=\"false\" data-action=\"like\" data-width=\"90\" data-height=\"25\" data-font=\"arial\" data-href=\"http://www.richiego.tw/cloud/10210/cvtc02/food/?page_id=4\" data-send=\"false\"></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"tweet_iframe_widget\" style=\"width: 62px; height: 25px;\"><iframe id=\"twitter-widget-0\" class=\"twitter-share-button twitter-share-button-rendered twitter-tweet-button\" style=\"position: absolute; visibility: hidden; width: 0px; height: 0px;\" title=\"Twitter Tweet Button\" src=\"http://http://platform.twitter.com/platform.twitter.com/widgets/tweet_button.57ff0b891fe1c9c735cbb440e7fd97ef.zh-tw.html#dnt=false&amp;id=twitter-widget-0&amp;lang=zh-tw&amp;original_referer=http%3A%2F%2F192.168.10.201%2Ffood%2F-page_id%3D4.htm&amp;size=m&amp;text=%E5%BA%97%E5%AE%B6%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9%20&amp;time=1716861815582&amp;type=share&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.richiego.tw%2Fcloud%2F10210%2Fcvtc02%2Ffood%2F%3Fpage_id%3D4\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" data-url=\"http://www.richiego.tw/cloud/10210/cvtc02/food/?page_id=4\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- #comments -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<!--more-->', '店家介紹', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '177-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-05-28 12:56:01', '2024-05-28 04:56:01', '', 177, 'http://192.168.10.79/food028/?p=207', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
